The paper discusses video streaming over distributed systems, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of erasure codes for reliability suggests a focus on networking and communication (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The optimization problem formulation and solution suggest a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
